## **Introduction**
Welcome to **Stage 0** of the **HackBio BioCoding Internship**! This stage focuses on setting up our team and structuring information in a data-friendly format. As bioinformatics enthusiasts, we organize data using **Python and R**, preparing for more advanced tasks ahead.

